{
  "texts": [
    "In some cases, such malicious parties might use the generated images to mislead viewers.",
    "This is a common issue in generative model approaches or content manipulation techniques.",
    "The details of the benchmarks are as follows:",
    "• ARC-c/e (Clark et al., 2018): the Challenge Set and Easy Set of ARC dataset of genuine grade-school level, containing 2376/1172 multiple-choice science questions in the test set, respectively.",
    "• OBQA (Mihaylov et al., 2018): questions requiring multi-step reasoning, use of additional commonsense knowledge, and rich text comprehension."
  ]
}